headline: 128th Common Stock Monthly Dividend Increase Declared by Realty Income
summary: Realty Income Corporation (Realty Income, NYSE: O), The Monthly Dividend Company®, today announced it has declared an increase in the company's common stock monthly cash dividend to $0.2640 per share from $0.2635 per share. The dividend is payable on January 15, 2025, to stockholders of record as of January 2, 2025. This is the 128th dividend increase since Realty Income's listing on the NYSE in 1994.
